docs.lead_paragraph: THE American Museum of Natural History, 100 years old this year, will be accorded a somewhat late postal recognition of its century of cultural and scientific achievements. Some time next year, hopefully before April 9, when the centennial ends, a block of four stamps will be issued, each depicting a subject of natural history.

docs.snippet: Italy defeated East Germany 3-0 in Naples yesterday and gained a berth in the World Cup soccer tournament to be held in Mexico City next summer. The teams had gone into the final qualifying round with 5 points each.
